'''細鹿屬'''（[[學名|學名]]''Leptotragulus''）是一[[屬|屬]]已[[滅絕|滅絕]]及細小的[[原角鹿科|原角鹿科]]。牠們生存於[[始新世|始新世]]的[[北美洲|北美洲]]。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://paleodb.org/cgi-bin/bridge.pl?action=checkTaxonInfo&taxon_no=42577&is_real_user=1 |title=PaleoBiology Database |access-date=2010-02-12 |archive-date=2012-10-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121014035301/http://paleodb.org/cgi-bin/bridge.pl?action=checkTaxonInfo&taxon_no=42577&is_real_user=1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>牠們外觀像[[鹿|鹿]]，但卻較為接近[[駱駝|駱駝]]。牠們頭上及眼眶上都有角。牠們重約8.79-11.1公斤。<ref>{{Cite journal en|author=M. Mendoza, C. M. Janis, and P. Palmqvist|year=2006|title=Estimating the body mass of extinct ungulates: a study on the use of multiple regression|journal=Journal of Zoology|volume=270|issue=1|pages=90-101}}</ref>

